{"tid":2283893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"煲底市集個Jack識唔識做生意架 真金白銀搞生意失業都唔養返自己","createTime":"2020-11-13T02:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T14:10:06.000Z","uid":5378,"like":186,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"143513e65979ca74e15fd851100274cd19e35cc4","tid":2283893,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:07:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/EHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FEHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=50035415\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201113%2FEHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE%2F&h=a439fc8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201113/EHIILUBZIBEBXB5DUY3KOPR6RE/</a><br />\n<br />\n同樣被裁走、加入國泰逾12年的艙務長Jack，就有較為充份的準備，「早幾個月預計到航空界會越嚟越差，外國其他航空公司已經開始炒緊人，有啲已經叫做破產、執咗啊，國泰難聽講句唔能夠獨善其身」。更新CV、留意就業市場情況等已屬基本，亦在10月起先後於兩間餐廳覓得炒散工作，一星期返足6日，「始終都要交租，平時要食飯，屋企仲有隻貓要養。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上Jack在正職以外另有副業，<span class=\"red\">年初與另外3個夥伴一同投資40萬元，成立網店「煲底市集」，加入並壯大黃色經濟圈，聘請同路人</span>，現時已收支平衡，「我身邊朋友問我：『咦，其實你自己有生意喎，點解仲要出去返part time呢？』」<span class=\"red\">但他稱寧願辛苦一點，都要堅持最初宗旨，「始終好希望我哋賺到嚿錢，一分一毫都盡力用喺手足身上面，如果變返養自己咁就冇咗個意思。」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n自己份工都保唔住寧願自己返六日炒散<br />\n都想檔生意優先幫返手足先<br />\n而唔係好似光時班管理層咁<br />\n一蚊都無出過就袋十幾萬一個月<br />\n用手足既錢幫自己供貴樓換新車<br />\nJack老闆咁樣做生意點得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多連登手足起碼都like返佢page支持下<br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/StandWithHongKongFairish/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FStandWithHongKongFairish%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=9a460fef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/StandWithHongKongFairish/</a><br />\n<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/stand_with_hong_kong_fairish\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstand_with_hong_kong_fairish&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2Byq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=2bed5a91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/stand_with_hong_kong_fairish</a><br />\n<br />\nLike完記得順手unlike光時檔垃圾page<br />\n將一分一毫用返係有良心既黃店上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5004ebbdf778b5680f0eccea8b92e864e59d6395","tid":2283893,"uid":327593,"like":14,"dislike":26,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:09:57.000Z","msg":"老實佢講咁既心態唔會做得長"},{"pid":"023bce6b9f876b7b147bc0416160f18a29ce45af","tid":2283893,"uid":334720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ec4f42618c9066cae585281defb7dca27cdd63","tid":2283893,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"條link係咪錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9453673ad5ca96585dd3497f106a4988549b0a","tid":2283893,"uid":5378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2ec4f42618c9066cae585281defb7dca27cdd63","tid":2283893,"uid":180851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"條link係咪錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T02:26:46.000Z","msg":"無錯喎 的確係內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"3eff354cddf54c336d3c71d55396d855c04d290e","tid":2283893,"uid":5378,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"5004ebbdf778b5680f0eccea8b92e864e59d6395","tid":2283893,"uid":327593,"like":14,"dislike":26,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"reply